    <comment>############

Please stage separately from 'gcc', this should fix the build on s390x,
unbreaking the zSystems repository.  It should also speedup Ring-0
builds significantly due to switching to release checking.

############

- Update to 16.0.1+git8152
- Avoids intermittent ABI breakage for libgccjit

- Switch to release checking

- Update to 16.0.1+git8070
- Revert s390x PGO bootstrap-lto-lean workaround.

- Avoid PGO bootstrap-lto-lean on s390x because of PR124406.

- Package libquadmath independently of fortran</comment>
